  39:../../../libs/libDaisy/src/sys/../../../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****     /** Sets the Mode for the DAC channels.
  40:../../../libs/libDaisy/src/sys/../../../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****      **
  41:../../../libs/libDaisy/src/sys/../../../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****      ** Polling mode uses the blocking mode to transmit a single value at a time.
